#
# Per-sample TMB computation (t093 / t081.2 / plan task 2).
#
# Computes per-sample mutation_count (protein-altering only), tmb, tmb_log10,
# panel_callable_mb, tmb_source, and propagates study_id as a first-class column
# (F3 fix). Emits a NEW file (samples_tmb.feather) so that existing consumers of
# samples.feather continue to see the original schema until they opt in.
#
